{
  "stem": "3605.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And a little time went by, and I was still in that ghetto.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And in January, they caught me again, with a transport of other women that were actually legal, there, too.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And they said that this is going someplace to a working place.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "Of course, I didn't believe him, but I was caught, and there was no recourse.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "There was nothing to bribe them with, and I had no means.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And-- and I was already tired of that living illegal, day from day, and being dependent and so on.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "And, sure enough, lucky for me, that transport didn't go to destruction.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "It went to an ammunition factory in Skarzysko-- HASAG.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "This was ammunition factories.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "This was also in central Poland.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Skarzysko is S-K-A-R-Z-Y-S-K-O.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "HASAG.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was H-A-S-A-G.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was Werk A.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This was-- they had in Skarzysko three different factories where different people where working at different things.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was working at the Werk A.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I was working by [NON-ENGLISH], which means the shells for the pistol-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For the pistol-- um-- guns.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "These were the small guns-- the little ones.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were very little, maybe an inch and a half, and a half a centimeter wide and so.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And later on, in a different department, they made the fillings-- the caps for the bullet.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this was-- that department was making the bullets.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In fact, later on, when I again got my Zionist connections-- we had connections wherever I-- somehow we gravitated to one another, and we found each other.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we had a contact with-- out of the ghetto, but this was a different contact, through certain Polish people.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there were also certain groups that went out of the-- not ghetto-- of the camp.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they were in the bau kommando.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
